[SN]TITLE[SN]
Craig Davies: Scunthorpe sign Wigan striker until end of 2016-17 season

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Scunthorpe United have signed Wigan striker Craig Davies on a deal until the end of the season.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 30-year-old former Wales international made 14 appearances for the Latics this term.
He could make his debut for the Iron in Saturday's League One game against struggling Bury, having been named on the bench.
Graham Alexander's side are third in the table, one point behind second-placed Bolton.
